text: Alexandra Hollá (born 24 October 1994) is a Slovak footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Slovakia women's national team. ==Career== Hollá has been capped for the Slovakia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak women's footballers Category:Slovakia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:ŠK Slovan Bratislava (women) players
